article.description: — Asbjorn Midtgaard had 16 points and 16 rebounds to carry Grand Canyon to an 81-71 win over Seattle on Saturday night.
article.headline: Midtgaard carries Grand Canyon over Seattle 81-71
article.linkText: Midtgaard carries Grand Canyon over Seattle 81-71
article.story: SEATTLE -- — Asbjorn Midtgaard had 16 points and 16 rebounds to carry Grand Canyon to an 81-71 win over Seattle on Saturday night. Jovan Blacksher Jr. had 17 points and seven assists for Grand Canyon (14-5, 8-2 Western Athletic Conference). Alessandro Lever and Mikey Dixon added 14 points apiece. Midtgaard made 10 of 12 from the free-throw line. Darrion Trammell had 28 points for the Redhawks (10-9, 3-4). Riley Grigsby added 25 points. The Antelopes evened the season series against the Redhawks. Seattle defeated Grand Canyon 63-57 on Friday. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
